Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------PREV------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两舷减速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维持既定高度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推进系统 地球航行模式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 索敌系统没有报警
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周边未发现高危目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰当前 正取道这条航线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向失落楼兰移动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预计两天后抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据称各部队正在当地集结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为向它发动总攻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.69,0:00:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我们抵达基地后也将参战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么不慌不忙地行进 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 我是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果飞得更高 速度更快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用一天就可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为避免被轨道上空的敌人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过计算敌人的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拟定的最佳航线和速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的行动一旦被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅殃及失落楼兰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.22,0:01:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战目的也会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 关于抵达后的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰底发生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量红外线反应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人袭击！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星移民计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因其失败被遗留在火星圈的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称独立国家维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向地球联邦政府宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争开始 已将近70年
