Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到从砂中发动突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显示出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂中移动的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过影像分析发现有18台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时有微弱的电子干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初步认定为集团作战的无人机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外暂无发现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候真佩服维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开发出这么适应地球环境的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想没用的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这确实值得深思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他们拥有比联邦先进的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以隐身衣为代表的高科技又是从何而来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这神秘感令人欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在重在想方设法应对敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管侥幸逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号却付出推进系统受损的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动能力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有件事让我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有机动战士出现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚看到新来的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘武装暴动当时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里附近航行的联邦战舰与敌人遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其后失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽曾派救援部队前往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后者亦下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据遇敌战舰最后的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人是三台机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总计两艘战舰和十台机动战士被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总部将其归类为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真身不明的敌人部队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后称为「幻影3」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影3…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙漠的亡灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这情报为什么现在才来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 别动气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 现在清楚一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人肯定会卷土重来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以必须用尽能用的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 所有机动战士更换成沙漠型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其次…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷他们在谈什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在那里干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤诺亚姑姑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？你在这艘船上做卫生员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星上接到的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙这忙那的没来得及告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到能和姑姑乘上同一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高兴能和爸爸还有你在同艘船上工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 罗玛丽和妈妈有消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是在附近城市里避难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧也该和她们联系一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 无非就是叫我下船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做父母的都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗 快逃 哈罗 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让它逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 听见没！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 吉欧 尤诺亚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难为你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这身打扮是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 现在忙不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂不是学过医疗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她在我身边帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一份工作就是照顾孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 原来这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 原来在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜路亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长叫我指导你 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伍德比特 接下来是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 刚来就这么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 能亲眼见识洛蒂师傅的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉提高特别大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 错了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说几遍才记住？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看模拟战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被训得挺惨的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧跟你年龄相仿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又都是新人 要好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 动手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住 时刻保持移动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握敌人位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火后也不能放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住这三点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然要我这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且和爷爷教的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太过重视攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简而言之就是太冒进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在教你怎么干掉对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是在战场求生的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 只守不攻没法取胜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是爷爷的教诲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果死了还谈什么胜负？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住战斗不只是冲锋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 休息几分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷摸摸躲在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还需要一阵子才能修完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说 队长？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就给它个下马威吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等摸清自动炮台的部署 它想逃也难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好 在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我们在检查它的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE构筑器？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 刚输入高达迄今为止的战斗记录
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是菲利特先生吩咐的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看能不能造出沙漠战需要的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然见过一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但像这样正式问候还是第一次吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫洛蒂·麦德纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船的工程主管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢那套机动战士对战模拟系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…和这位伍德比特跟明日野家有点缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我修过几次你爸的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的爷爷是菲利特先生的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的妈妈和你的爸爸还是同一个部队的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 不愧是英雄的孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年纪轻轻驾驶高达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还那么能打 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛蒂先生 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是叫伍德比特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫吉欧·明日野 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少得意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有得意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么明日野家族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算你爷爷是联邦军老司令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶过高达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当自己有多了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛蒂师傅他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是著名的麦德纳工坊的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他主动参军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一介士兵做到工程主管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论决心还是志向 你都没法和他比！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没资格跟他这么说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来 你崇拜洛蒂先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很崇拜爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 伍德比特君 想见见爷爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能学到不少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有完没完啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为所有人都会给你特殊待遇
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为什么那么生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 吉欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比休息前状态的还差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷真的是个很了不起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伍德比特如果了解爷爷的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实谁也不想看到你这样的孩子上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜路亚小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论有多严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是想你在战斗中生还
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 这话从何说起？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是情绪低落？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 只是分心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样比较容易让孩子安心 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 是我误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,执行岗哨任务的乔纳森机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在砂中发现移动物体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数量3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待命中的机师请准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs52}来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达的新部件如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解析完成 但还在构筑中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离完成还要一定时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有赶上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得已了 用AGE-3出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狩猎时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿比斯队 按准备会的部署行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和乔纳森 德雷克在上空吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜路亚和奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁定无人机位置后攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇·阿比斯 克兰修特装型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不可以飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知敌人藏在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样只会变成活靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇他们已经去承担这份职责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你专心摧毁无人机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙漠型也显得行动缓慢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧·明日野 高达出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心 机体容易陷入砂里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁愿放慢动作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要保持机体平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了 是高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极品猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包围它！痛扁它！歼灭它！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三角攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 下沉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特先生 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新武器 G气垫战机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 立即发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行空中换装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空中换装…机师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛蒂师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是开动它的话 我也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维修班不能没有洛蒂师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伍德比特！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他随随便便就能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定也能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别紧张 细节交给自动驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伍德比特·甘海尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,G气垫战机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管它呢 打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 空中换装！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为我们会看着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 快完成合体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是AGE-3 要塞模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住这3点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次三角攻击送他归天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持运动为的是不被敌人瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死 到处乱窜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍小聪明的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时刻掌握敌人位置的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既容易躲避攻击 也容易反击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火以后也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 老夫果然没看错你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 大家 快躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伍德比特君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伍德比特…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么客气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我伍德比特就可以了 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安息吧 兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定为你报这个仇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜路亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了一台幻影3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜路亚小姐教我的 真的很管用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台被击落的机动战士里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是人在驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可他们是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人也有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争不是什么值得高兴的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜路亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜路亚很少说起自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在战争中失去了父母
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说妹妹也重病缠身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却在她面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次次为敌人伤心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人会疯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为胜利高兴并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
